     C                     KFLD           S@MCN
     C           K#FCX     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           D@PRT1
     C                     KFLD           D@PRT2
     C                     KFLD           D@PRT3
     C                     KFLD           S@PROC
     C                     KFLD           S@MCN
     C                     KFLD           K@YMD
